title: DDFP 410: Week 13 review & Playoff Picture preview
itunes:title: DDFP 410: Week 13 review & Playoff Picture preview
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank to recap the Monday Night Football matchup between the Cowboys and Redskins, as well as break down the NFC playoff picture. Then, Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew join the show to discuss potential 2016 coaching changes, the AFC wild card contenders and MJD's thoughts on whether or not J.J. Watt is overrated.
